        {
            "id": 6076409,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉漲逾百點拉回平盤整理 電子熄火資金再度回流傳產",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股今 (25) 日開盤後走高一度漲逾百點，不過隨後急殺翻黑，上沖下洗震盪逾 150 點，今日估量約 3200 億元。在電子股熄火下，資金再度回流傳產族群，包括鋼鐵、航運等均走強。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6076409/l/171d882f660b83c6f56b7f99310fed94.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股開盤〉漲逾百點後急殺翻黑 電子熄火資金再度回流傳產。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 今日開盤上漲 10 元、開 1155 元，早盤暫在平盤上震盪，昨日扮演多頭要角的鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 今日開高走低，早盤翻黑震盪，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>)、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>)、廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 等電子權值也在平盤下震盪。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>傳產族群表現強勢，鋼鐵指標大成鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2027:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2027\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2027-TW</a>) 漲半根停板，中鋼 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2002:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2002-TW</a>) 同步走揚，台塑四寶則以南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>) 最為強勢，與旗下南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>) 均漲逾 4%，航空雙雄及貨櫃三雄、水泥雙雄均呈現上漲。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>重電指標華城 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1519:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1519\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1519-TW</a>) 也漲逾 3%，另外，研華 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2395:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2395\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2395-TW</a>)、漢唐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2404:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2404\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2404-TW</a>) 漲約 2%，英業達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2356:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2356\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2356-TW</a>) 也上漲，為早盤相對有撐的電子股則有</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6076409",
